    <section class="ahead">
      <div class="eyebrow">Jun 10, 2023 · Brunch Club</div>
      <h1>Talk &amp; Bottomless Brunch with Self Love London</h1>
      <p class="lede">Empowering our inner-selves and strengthening our inner cheerleader.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="cover reveal"><img src="{{ 'group_morena-full.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Guests gathered at the bottomless brunch at Morena" loading="eager"></div>

    <section class="read">
      <div class="prose">
        <p class="first">If you are new here, welcome! The SAÏA Brunch Club is a monthly meet-up that features wellness, empowerment and delicious food. This gathering is the perfect way to celebrate sisterhood, learn from each other, and create meaningful connections with amazing women.</p>
        <p>This edition we took over the vibrant <a href="https://morenalondon.com/" rel="noopener">Morena</a>, a hidden gem in Eccleston Yards in the heart of Victoria. The colourful and bright interiors were a perfect complement to our Latin-inspired bottomless brunch, opened by an insightful talk from Charlotte Black, founder of Self Love London.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="band duo reveal"><figure><img src="{{ 'Morena_1-L.png' | asset_url }}" alt="The colourful interiors of Morena in Eccleston Yards"><img src="{{ 'Morena_1-R.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Brunch table set at Morena"></figure></div>

    <section class="feat reveal">
      <div class="feat-in">
        <img src="{{ 'charlotte-L.png' | asset_url }}" alt="Charlotte Black, founder of Self Love London, speaking to guests" loading="lazy">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Our guest speaker</div>
          <h2>Charlotte Black</h2>
          <p>Charlotte is a soulful self-love coach and mentor whose mission is to support women to reconnect to their inner worth, self-love and confidence. She is the founder of <a href="https://www.instagram.com/selflovelondonuk/" rel="noopener">Self Love London</a>.</p>
          <p>Charlotte talked to us about her empowerment journey, reminding us of the importance of discovering and amplifying our inner cheerleaders. She introduced a beautiful metaphor: each of us has four inner voices — our Cheerleader, our Critic, our Witness and our Constructive Critic. Her talk helped us boost our confidence and turn down the volume on our inner critic.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="read">
      <div class="chapter reveal"><span class="t">The menu</span><span class="rule"></span></div>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>A Latin-inspired bottomless brunch menu, paired with bubbly mimosas at Morena. This brunch came with a vegetarian twist as we introduced delicious fluffy pancakes and a refreshing açaí bowl — plus your favourite brunch staples, from avo toast to freshly baked pastries.</p>
        <p>A delicious selection to choose from as you enjoyed the sunshine in Eccleston Yard's piazza.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="band duo reveal"><figure><img src="{{ 'morena_1_44e3117e-95e8-4eef-aed7-39e9dbef50cb-R.png' | asset_url }}" alt="The Latin-inspired brunch spread at Morena" loading="lazy"><img src="{{ 'morena_1_44e3117e-95e8-4eef-aed7-39e9dbef50cb-L.png' | asset_url }}" alt="The SAÏA menu card at the Morena brunch" loading="lazy"><figcaption>Bottomless brunch · Morena, Eccleston Yards</figcaption></figure></div>

    <section class="close reveal">
      <p>As always, the SAÏA Brunch Club is designed so that every guest gets the opportunity to network and connect over a beautifully prepared brunch.</p>
